# Fuzz Corpus Directory
#
# This directory stores serialized failing inputs discovered during
# fuzz testing. When a fuzz test fails, proptest auto-saves the
# failing case to proptest-regressions/ (parent directory).
#
# This directory contains manually-curated corpus entries:
# - JSON files with serialized ContractAction sequences
# - Replayable as deterministic regression tests in fuzz_tests.rs
#
# See FUZZ_FINDINGS.md for a log of all discoveries.
